{"tid":2345173,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"《虛構政府》項目測試議題，《虛構警隊》","createTime":"2020-12-29T09:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T09:49:13.000Z","uid":298288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3c906e6eb0adc4285205f8c7cfb001cde195c829","tid":2345173,"uid":298288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:46:52.000Z","msg":"繼前文論及關於《虛構政府》的可能性<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2341805/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2341805/</a><br />\n<br />\n試試引起一下大家比較喜聞樂見的警隊議題<br />\n如果重新建設一個警隊，它應該是怎樣的？<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/18m5rUPFKzepxGSyc6pBomQnhbPTXUecQuVztaRy9114/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fpresentation%2Fd%2F18m5rUPFKzepxGSyc6pBomQnhbPTXUecQuVztaRy9114%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=fc0b0fab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/18m5rUPFKzepxGSyc6pBomQnhbPTXUecQuVztaRy9114/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n先整理了部分警隊特徵以及歷史遺留的問題，當然並不完全啦，如果一個人做完所有野就會俾人一種已經完成品的錯覺，但當中絕對會有錯誤，又因爲完成品的錯覺而令人忽略了當中的謬誤，所以不如將半成品拿出來俾大家討論、修改、完善，結果可能更好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cdy9vW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cdy9vW.png&h=52e8f2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/214VDpe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F214VDpe.png&h=c0a9d8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KjwwWaY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKjwwWaY.png&h=cf7c0392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yW5RbKj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyW5RbKj.png&h=7c4511ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AKZB7hF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAKZB7hF.png&h=74dfe79d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76c55018191f733b640a28ff24d215c86f2168e0","tid":2345173,"uid":298288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:49:13.000Z","msg":"如果國安法判定呢個唔講得，記得提我收皮，費事我仲傻更更繼續講呢D俾人拉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}